{"tid":2209242,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[估國家] 小學保安在監護人眼皮底下侵犯7歲女童","createTime":"2020-09-19T13:34:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T13:43:32.000Z","uid":231132,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f5a60025f03d41463c1860471866357ab4c96b89","tid":2209242,"uid":231132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T13:34:51.000Z","msg":"今年5月份，北京某小學發生一起學校保安猥褻2名女童案件。<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/sinakd2020919s/41/w973h668/20200919/3ae4-izmihnt2218387.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fsinakd2020919s%2F41%2Fw973h668%2F20200919%2F3ae4-izmihnt2218387.jpg&h=062f8c57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嫌疑人在教室用嘴蹭被害人臉部、頸部，並將其中一名7歲女童，帶至另一間教室撫摸其胸部。<br />\n<br />\n據辦案檢察官介紹，該案犯罪嫌疑人的行為涉嫌猥褻兒童罪，同時其屬對未成年人負有特殊職責的人員，應從嚴懲處。<br />\n<br />\n目前該案已被提起公訴。"},{"pid":"282813ed9d4d97c6a3b344cc438a27772876e57e","tid":2209242,"uid":110656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T13:36:08.000Z","msg":"新北市呢期唔爭氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2733d848835f8faa80ac43cf3263f02e3113591","tid":2209242,"uid":55458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T13:36:19.000Z","msg":"貝晶強姦妮"},{"pid":"29e73d941eec3ab5a05bc11d88b04d1fecdc81a5","tid":2209242,"uid":231132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"282813ed9d4d97c6a3b344cc438a27772876e57e","tid":2209242,"uid":110656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T13:36:08.000Z","msg":"新北市呢期唔爭氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T13:43:20.000Z","msg":"超台趕印<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a984f8934cdbd17e4cfc64d2fd612c07ed172332","tid":2209242,"uid":231132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2733d848835f8faa80ac43cf3263f02e3113591","tid":2209242,"uid":55458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T13:36:19.000Z","msg":